
\faDiamond\ \textlcsc{ \textcolor{dgreen}{\Large \textbf{Study Check}} }\\
Construct the electron-dot structure of \ce{NH3} indicating the number of bonds and lone pairs.
\providetoggle{long}\settoggle{long}{false}\iftoggle{long}{}{\begin{flushright} \mytriangleright{dgreen}\small 
 Answer: \chemfig{\lewis{2,N}( (-[:0]H)(-[:180]H)(-[:270]H))}; three bonds and one lone pair.
 \end{flushright} }